dataIdentifierInThisTmplDesc: The identifiers in this template will be used in sensitive data discovery job.
platFormWillLabel: The platform will label data catalog with privacy tag
dataMatches: if data matches the enabled data identifier’s rule.
dataScaned: if data is scanned, but not matched with any of enabled data identifiers.
dataNeverScanned: If a data is never scanned, the privacy tag shows “N/A”
defineClassificationDesc: A classification template contains a set of data identifiers. Sensitive data discovery job uses a classification template to identify sensitive data.
